thread.title: Names and Games: Tuesday, Sept. 29, 2015

author: Messenger-Inquirer
title: Names and Games: Tuesday, Sept. 29, 2015
text:
What: 2015 Open-Club Championship (includes senior division for ages 55 and up) 
Cost: $50 for members, $65 for non-members. Seniors $40 for members and $50 for non-members. 
When: Oct. 10-11. 
Where: Panther Creek Golf Course 
Note: Entry cost includes green fee, cart fee and Sunday lunch. Complimentary practice round comes with paid entry (must purchase cart). Players not able to play Saturday can make arrangements to play earlier in the week. Prizes include trophy for both division winners, an estimated $500 ($300 for senior division), gift certificates, golf apparel and accessories, etc. 
Contact: Patrick Schirmer, (270) 401-4244 or pgschirmer@gmail.com Ã—
